collation.p:
The manuscript consists of 10 quires: one bifolium, one
                                        senion and eight quaternions. Kk.6.23.1: quires 1-7;
                                        Kk.6.23.2: quires 8-10.

handNote.p:
Guillaume Budé added some marginal corrections to the text
                                    throughtout: Kk.6.23.1 f. 22v, 27r;
                                    Kk.6.23.2 ff. 3r, 4r, 8r, 9r.
